is.free.fr/Essays/Commedia.html |last=Palleschi|first=Marino |title= The Commedia dell'Arte: Its Origins, Development & Influence on the Ballet|language=Italian|date=5 December 2005|accessdate=6 January 2009|ref=harv}} * Tannen, D. (1984). ''Conversational style: Analyzing talk among friends.'' Norwood, NJ: [[Ablex Publishing]]. {{ISBN|0-19-522181-8}} * Tannen, D. (1990). ''You just don’t understand: Men and women in conversation.'' New York: Ballantine. {{ISBN|978-0-06-095962-3}} * Thomas, J. A. (1983). "Cross-cultural pragmatic failure." ''[[Applied Linguistics (journal)|Applied Linguistics]]'', 4, 91-112. ISSN 0142-6001 * Westacott, E. (2006). "The Rights and Wrongs of Rudeness." International Journal of Applied Philosophy, 20:1. * {{cite web |url=http://www.slate.com/articles/life/explainer/2013/01/eye_rolling_why_do_people_roll_their_eyes_when_they_re_annoyed.html|last=Wickman|first=Forrest|title=Oh, Please: When did we start rolling our eyes to express contempt?|date=15 January 2013|website=Slate|ref=harv}}
